Package: catfda
Type: Package
Title: Categorical Functional Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Your", "Name", email = "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Co-Author", "Name", email = "coauthor@example.com", role = "aut")
)
Description: A comprehensive package for analyzing categorical functional data.
    Provides methods for estimating latent Gaussian processes and probability curves
    from categorical time series data using various link functions including probit,
    binomial, and multinomial approaches. Supports both sequential and parallel
    computation for efficient analysis of large datasets.
